
                                            Eastern Cape police are searching for a 55-year-old woman who disappeared after her boyfriend was found murdered in Coega.
                                         CAPE TOWN - Eastern Cape police are searching for a 55-year-old woman who disappeared after her boyfriend was found murdered in Coega. The man had sustained fatal head wounds.  The police’s Andre Beetge says: “Anybody with information of her whereabouts or information about this murder is requested to contact their nearest police station.”